it just goes boom in India and we just enjoy that, we don’t want anything else and it is so difficult

00:40:45.000 --> 00:40:48.892
for them to send them to send back to their own country that you actually push them with a pistol,

00:40:49.000 --> 00:40:53.892
now go back. And they enjoy all the discomfort in that country

00:40:54.000 --> 00:40:57.892
I was surprised absolutely most uncomfortable places there.

