everything plastic, even for towels you have plastic at least in India you have everything cotton.

00:41:27.000 --> 00:41:31.892
You have a plate of say, a beautiful plate of brass to eat food,

00:41:32.000 --> 00:41:34.892
what do you have in your country that you are talking of your comfort

00:41:35.000 --> 00:41:37.892
and they got a little bit I said at least we have motor cars, all right

00:41:38.000 --> 00:41:44.892
we have got bullock carts doesn’t matter but it is too much for them to go by a bullock cart

00:41:45.000 --> 00:41:49.892
because you see their body is all shaken up and their attention all outside you see.

00:41:50.000 --> 00:41:52.892
So this is what happens your attention becomes balanced,

00:41:53.000 --> 00:41:57.892
attention becomes collectively conscious you start enjoying others

00:41:58.000 --> 00:42:03.892
and this so called comfort which we really vie is zero.

00:42:04.000 --> 00:42:10.892
