00:42:11.000 --> 00:42:16.892
For a holiday and the people from Brighton have came to Yorkshire for a holiday.

00:42:17.000 --> 00:42:21.892
I said. But why? I can’t understand they can’t sit in the house you see nothing like a Grahasta,

00:42:22.000 --> 00:42:24.892
means the one who stays in the house is there,

00:42:25.000 --> 00:42:26.892
there’s nothing like a householder they are always out,

00:42:27.000 --> 00:42:31.892
out of the house as soon as they get holiday they must pack up and go out,

00:42:32.000 --> 00:42:34.892
some people are just cruising. Why? Why are you cruising?

00:42:35.000 --> 00:42:39.892
You must sit at home, home is the place of bliss, sit down,

00:42:40.000 --> 00:42:43.892
talk together and have some rapport, be nice to each other.

00:42:44.000 --> 00:42:46.892
That’s not there you will have a television in between you,

00:42:47.000 --> 00:42:49.892
otherwise if there is no television there is a fight.

00:42:50.000 --> 00:42:54.892
