00:42:55.000 --> 00:42:58.892
you have television or a newspaper or something in between.

00:42:59.000 --> 00:43:03.892
There’s nothing like enjoying the company of another person. Why?

00:43:04.000 --> 00:43:08.892
Because our attention is so shaky, it just gets disturbed for nothing at all,

00:43:09.000 --> 00:43:13.892
I mean how can you live in a place, in any place without any sound?

00:43:14.000 --> 00:43:18.892
You want to have a soundless area then why God as given you ears?

00:43:19.000 --> 00:43:23.892
See He has given you the ears to enjoy the music of his rhythm and that you can only feel

00:43:24.000 --> 00:43:28.892
when you become a realised soul before that you are very uncomfortable,

00:43:29.000 --> 00:43:35.892
you have all kinds of wrinkles all over, and you ask them why have you got wrinkles?

00:43:36.000 --> 00:43:40.892
Oh God, you know I have neighbours who are young boys, they are all the time singing loudly,

00:43:41.000 --> 00:43:45.892
I will grow old in no time. I said I would go and join them if it was so,

00:43:46.000 --> 00:43:50.892
what is there to feel so bad about it? What is there to feel that you cannot bear it?

00:43:51.000 --> 00:43:53.892
