00:43:54.000 --> 00:43:56.892
Because our attention makes us tired all the time our attention is,

00:43:57.000 --> 00:44:02.892
and the worst is our attention is on the watch. Watching the time, for what?

00:44:03.000 --> 00:44:08.892
For what are you watching the time, there is no more going to be a war of Waterloo anything.

00:44:09.000 --> 00:44:13.892
You don’t have to worry on that point, when the bomb will come, it will come without knowing;

00:44:14.000 --> 00:44:19.892
so why watch the time? After all that’s the only thing that is important isn’t it,

00:44:20.000 --> 00:44:26.892
otherwise what is important, is enjoy the time, this moment, every moment has a dynamism in it.

00:44:27.000 --> 00:44:30.892
