But I tell you for a Sahaja Yogi the trains will stop, the aeroplanes will stop;

00:44:38.000 --> 00:44:42.892
everything stops for them. Because after all its all God’s realm you are entering into.

00:44:43.000 --> 00:44:46.892
Who is greater than God, who is more powerful than Him,

00:44:47.000 --> 00:44:52.892
once you enter into His Kingdom everything works out, you know it works out.

00:44:53.000 --> 00:44:55.892
Mother we don’t know how it worked out, it works out.

00:44:56.000 --> 00:44:58.892
They talk in third person, it works out.

00:44:59.000 --> 00:45:07.892
So the joy of those happenings, the joy of that blissfullness,

00:45:08.000 --> 00:45:12.892
that security of God, fills you up and when it fills you up

00:45:13.000 --> 00:45:19.892
you feel absolutely relaxed. You feel it’s all done for you.

