because I think he’s a possessed person and with me sitting here sometimes you know,

00:45:31.000 --> 00:45:34.892
they go into contortions and do all kinds of things, better that he’s gone.

00:45:35.000 --> 00:45:39.892
But you don’t pay attention to him, he’s nothing important, there’s no need to turn your eyes.

00:45:40.000 --> 00:45:43.892
Just now were talking something nice, lets talk of something nice,

00:45:44.000 --> 00:45:45.892
why put the attention to something that’s not so nice.

00:45:46.000 --> 00:45:53.892
So attention should be at the nice things as we say but it is never. How do we do?

00:45:54.000 --> 00:45:58.892
We do it by enjoying the nice things, by understanding the nice things,

00:45:59.000 --> 00:46:04.892
just our attention goes there and whatever else may be there we just don’t see, we just don’t see.

00:46:05.000 --> 00:46:13.892
We once went to a place called Nepal, you must have heard about Nepal and Kathmandu

00:46:14.000 --> 00:46:18.892
and my daughters were there with me and normally Indian people are a little bit,

00:46:19.000 --> 00:46:21.892
sort of you see with daughters, they would not carry them to places

00:46:22.000 --> 00:46:25.892
if there are erotics and all that, actually we had never seen erotics in all our lives you see

00:46:26.000 --> 00:46:27.892
because our attention is not there.

00:46:28.000 --> 00:46:31.892
So we saw the whole of Nepal we never saw any erotics you see,

00:46:32.000 --> 00:46:35.892
second time I went my disciple was there he was writing a book

00:46:36.000 --> 00:46:39.892
and he said Mother do you know that Nepal has the maximum number of erotics?

00:46:40.000 --> 00:46:43.892
I said no, I never saw. We were moving about with our daughters

00:46:44.000 --> 00:46:45.892
we had never seen any erotics anywhere.

00:46:46.000 --> 00:46:49.892
Oh it’s full with that. I said where on top of every temple

00:46:50.000 --> 00:46:52.892
I said why do you see the top of the temple, why don’t you see inside the temple,

00:46:53.000 --> 00:46:56.892
he said no on top of the temple you’ll find lots of these erotics.

00:46:57.000 --> 00:47:03.892
I said where? You know to my amazement when we went there the Japanese had put up,

00:47:04.000 --> 00:47:14.892
long, these wires and what you call them, what you call them those big machine like ladders,

00:47:15.000 --> 00:47:21.892
special ladders they have and with the zoom lenses they were taking photographs of these erotics.

00:47:22.000 --> 00:47:24.892
I said Baba what’s the matter with these?

00:47:25.000 --> 00:47:28.892
I said what is there to see in that, and they were taking photographs of these.

00:47:29.000 --> 00:47:33.892
I said from this distance I can’t see anything. I mean any Indian who goes there,

00:47:34.000 --> 00:47:39.892
goes to a temple, his attention is on the Deity and he’s not bothered we never saw these things.

00:47:40.000 --> 00:47:41.892
What is there outside?

00:47:42.000 --> 00:47:44.892
And these Japanese are there with the zoom there’s one falling down and holding onto the wire,

00:47:45.000 --> 00:47:50.892
another standing on his head trying to arrange the camera, to get what?

00:47:51.000 --> 00:47:58.892
That filth, dirt. I was amazed because our attention is used to filth,

00:47:59.000 --> 00:48:06.892
you see if you know people who are, called a sweepers in India, they have to clean the,

00:48:07.000 --> 00:48:12.892
which is not very good thing, but they do dirt cleaning thing, or the garbage cleaning;

00:48:13.000 --> 00:48:17.892
and they have no nose to feel the dirt or anything. You see they become like animals,

00:48:18.000 --> 00:48:19.892
they can pass through any dirt or filth.

