00:48:29.000 --> 00:48:32.892
That’s what we have lost sensitivity to sense

00:48:33.000 --> 00:48:38.892
but after realisation you just become sensitivity and you abhor it, you just leave it.

00:48:39.000 --> 00:48:41.892
