00:48:42.000 --> 00:48:46.892
You never enjoy a sinful act and the enjoyment of righteousness

00:48:47.000 --> 00:48:50.892
and virtue starts flowering into and you become flowering personality.

00:48:51.000 --> 00:48:53.892
