00:48:54.000 --> 00:48:58.892
or you never use this word I hate you and next movement I love you.

00:48:59.000 --> 00:49:01.892
That sort of a nonsense goes away from your tongue.

00:49:02.000 --> 00:49:06.892
You become beautiful person whose never bored, whose never bored.

00:49:07.000 --> 00:49:11.892
